@startuml Casos de Uso - E-commerce Frontend
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam actorStyle awesome

title Sistema E-commerce - Tienda Online

' Actores
actor "Cliente" as Customer

' Sistema
rectangle "Tienda Online (Cliente)" {
  
  package "Navegación" {
    usecase "Explorar Productos" as UC1
    usecase "Filtrar por\nCategoría/Marca" as UC2
    usecase "Buscar Productos" as UC3
    usecase "Ver Detalle\nde Producto" as UC4
  }
  
  package "Carrito de Compras" {
    usecase "Agregar al Carrito" as UC5
    usecase "Gestionar Carrito" as UC6
    usecase "Seleccionar Talle" as UC7
  }
  
  package "Checkout" {
    usecase "Realizar Checkout" as UC8
    usecase "Ingresar Datos\nde Envío" as UC9
    usecase "Confirmar Compra" as UC10
  }
  
  package "Soporte" {
    usecase "Contactar por\nWhatsApp" as UC11
    usecase "Ver Información\nde la Tienda" as UC12
  }
}

' Relaciones
Customer --> UC1
Customer --> UC2
Customer --> UC3
Customer --> UC4
Customer --> UC5
Customer --> UC6
Customer --> UC7
Customer --> UC8
Customer --> UC9
Customer --> UC10
Customer --> UC11
Customer --> UC12

' Notas
note right of UC5
  **Validación en tiempo real:**
  - Stock disponible
  - Stock por talle
  - Cálculo de totales
end note

note bottom of UC10
  **Confirmar Compra:**
  - Crea orden en backend
  - Valida stock final
  - Actualiza inventario
  - Genera número de orden
  
  Estado inicial: PENDING
end note

note left of UC11
  **WhatsApp:**
  Link directo con mensaje
  predefinido del producto
end note

@enduml
